name: Remembrance Day 'Poppies' Limited Edition Print*
description: A fine art print of the titled poppies. The original was drawn with coloured pencils and has proved a very popular image. All prints are professionally reproduced onto high quality 400gsm paper with a Matt finish, and all copies are signed and numbered (limited run of 20). Measurements are 16.5 x 11 Inches. *Until 11am on 11/11/11, 50% of each sale goes the Royal British Legion's Poppy Appeal. All orders will be sent out after this date.

name: 'Cat on the Horizon' Limited Edition Print
description: A fine art print of surreal drawing 'Cat on the Horizon', which depicts a cat walking across the skyline of Brighton, UK. Drawn with graphite pencil for submission to the Cambridge Drawing Society, in whose exhibition the original was sold. All prints are professionally reproduced onto high quality, 400gsm paper with a Matt finish. All are signed and numbered (limited run of 20). Measurements are 17.8 x 11.7 Inches.

name: 'Suburban' Limited Edition Print
description: A fine art print of the recent illustration 'Suburban'. Originally done in biro, with coloured pencils highlighting the blood. Based in the Stukeley Meadows neighbourhood in Huntingdon UK. All prints are professionally reproduced onto high-quality 400gsm paper with a Matt finish, and all are signed and numbered (limited run of 20). Measurements are 16.5 x 11.7 Inches.

name: 'Of the Darkness I Ask' Limited Edition Print
description: A fine art print of the above mentioned drawing. Drawn with graphite pencil in 2006, the orginal was based on a series of photographic self-portraits for A Level studies. All prints are professionally reproduced onto tactile 300gsm paper with a Matt finish, signed and numbered (limited run of 20). Measurements are 16.5 x 11.7 Inches.

name: 'Mothers Milk' Limited Editon Print
description: A fine art print of photograph 'Mothers Milk', an evocative still life image starring a wonky-eyed doll. What's not to like? All prints are professionally reproduced onto high-quality 400gsm paper with a Matt finish, and all are signed and numbered (limited run of 20). Measurements are 16.5 x 11 Inches.
